Embarking on a harrowing spiritual journey under the guidance of Gaia, the Earth-goddess, Brinke defeated P'Numbra at the cost of Arcana's life and saved the human race from summary execution by the arrogant, powerful celetial council.  But taht happily ever after thing can be a real bear...
